data.name: Apple of Enlightenment
data.desc: Target cards in your opponent's GY, up to the number of "Valkyrie" monsters you control; banish them. If this Set card in its owner's control has left the field because of an opponent's effect, and is now in the GY or banished: You can draw cards equal to the number of "Valkyrie" monsters you control +1.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
